2613
01:07:24,310 --> 01:07:25,480
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Panting)</font>

2614
01:07:26,280 --> 01:07:29,850
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He keeps rattling the stones with desperation in his heart.)</font>

2615
01:07:28,750 --> 01:07:30,020
<font size="64">I'm nearly done.</font>

2616
01:07:30,950 --> 01:07:32,290
<font size="64">Okay. Only a few pieces remain.</font>

2617
01:07:31,090 --> 01:07:32,450
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Emotional)</font>

2618
01:07:35,860 --> 01:07:37,690
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Super focused)</font>

2619
01:07:38,490 --> 01:07:39,690
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Breathing heavily)</font>

2620
01:07:39,360 --> 01:07:40,630
<font size="64">Only a few pieces remain.</font>

2621
01:07:41,960 --> 01:07:43,960
<font size="64">For goodness' sake.</font>

2622
01:07:44,270 --> 01:07:46,270
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The stone tower demolition crew shows up again.)</font>

2623
01:07:47,740 --> 01:07:49,340
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Tumbling down)</font>

2624
01:07:47,840 --> 01:07:49,440
<font size="64">What are you doing? Come on.</font>

2625
01:07:49,600 --> 01:07:51,570
<font size="64">What are you doing? Come on.</font>

2626
01:07:50,170 --> 01:07:52,770
