2632
01:08:01,950 --> 01:08:03,950
<font size="64">I need to make that tower to escape.</font>

2633
01:08:02,320 --> 01:08:04,750
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Clenching his teeth)</font>

2634
01:08:03,950 --> 01:08:05,650
