01:08:34,880 --> 01:08:36,250
<font size="64">- How much is a soda? - It's one dollar.</font>

2661
01:08:36,250 --> 01:08:37,420
<font size="64">- One dollar? - Yes.</font>

2662
01:08:37,420 --> 01:08:38,620
<font size="64">I'll drink one.</font>

2663
01:08:39,090 --> 01:08:40,150
<font size="64">For goodness' sake.</font>

