<font size="64">Look. MINNIE is in the background.</font>

2679
01:09:06,250 --> 01:09:10,850
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Se Chan is eating a nectarine, and MINNIE is behind him.)</font>

2680
01:09:07,350 --> 01:09:08,720
<font size="64">It's a photo of Se Chan,</font>

2681
