2698
01:09:44,390 --> 01:09:45,620
<font size="64">Wasn't this taken today?</font>

2699
01:09:46,050 --> 01:09:49,120
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Jae Seok and Jong Kook are on a tractor.)</font>

2700
01:09:49,460 --> 01:09:51,130
<font size="64">Jae Seok and Jong Kook?</font>

2701
01:09:53,690 --> 01:09:56,060
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(MIYEON finds a photo as well.)</font>

2702
01:09:56,200 --> 01:09:57,970
<font size="64">It's a photo of the nectarines.</font>

2703
01:09:58,170 --> 01:10:01,340
